name: Andy on SOL
description: Andy is solana blockchain. Fans of the Matt Furie and the boys club will love this. Plot the next course with me and my friends. It’s gonna be wild, unexpected, and totally epic. We’re here to play the game AND change the game. Stick with us, and who knows what adventures await? So, what’s it gonna be? Ready to ride the $ANDY wave? I won’t be crushed if you say no. But your wallet might be. This isn’t all about getting rich quick though (but hey, no complaints if we do). Come chill on the couch, let’s spark a good one and make some memories duuuuude! Feels good man.
